features: 👏Clean & Classic Design - The classic geometric element and simple modern construction give this SIHANM black storage cabinet a beautiful and all-matching look, the best to show off your taste. Understated and elegant and can be well-matched with other furniture and different interior decoration styles.

👏Ample Storage Space - This black cabinet with doors and shelves provides ample storage space for everyday accessories, tableware, and more. A movable shelf makes it easy to adapt the space to your storage needs. The spacious table top can hold some of your favorite small items such as photos, plants, aroma, key holder, etc.

👏High-Quality Material - The water-resistant finish on the laminated MDF and particleboard makes this buffet table perfect for adding storage to any room in your home. SIHANM sideboard cabinet is strong and stable, and the raised solid wooden legs prevent moisture damage and make it easier to keep the surface under your bathroom storage cabinet clean.

👏Multi-Usage Accent Cabinet - Not only can be placed in the bathroom, hallway, porch or living room, this buffet cabinet with storage can be used as a tall nightstand next to your bed or as a sideboard in the kitchen pantry to store your tableware. It is ideal for small spaces such as apartments and dorm rooms. The simple lines and unique handles give it a modern feel and are the best choice to decorate your living space.

👏Easy to Assemble - SIHANM black buffet cabinet comes with clear instructions that show illustrations and marked all the spare parts. If your item arrives damaged, scratched or missing part, please feel free to contact us, and we will send you free replacement or offer a partial refund.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Really sturdy and beautiful sideboards
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I bought two of these cabinets to use as bedside cabinets. I was surprised by how nice the faux bois finish felt, and how sturdy they seemed. I really like that the insides of the doors also have the finished chevron pattern and the cabinet door hinges are really solid and smooth. The cabinets were easy to build, took about 1 hour per cabinet. As I was building them, I kept thinking that whoever works in quality control should get a raise. EVERYTHING went together smoothly and lined up perfectly. That is no easy feat. I think the instructions could be improved with larger print of the letter labels, but that’s minor. 5 stars!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 26, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very nice quality for the price.
reviews.reviewText: Very nice cabinet. Easy to assemble. Great accent piece to a room

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 7, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to be for a little coffee station and it works well so far. I still need to get a mat for the top otherwise it holds all my coffee and accessories with no issues. It was pretty easy to put together. It comes with a small screwdriver, but you may want to get one a little larger in the handle so you don't get hand cramps from the twisting. I like that the hinges are adjustable so you can make the doors fit better versus just simple hinges that aren’t adjustable. Only downside to this is that there is not plastic or felt covers for the feet. There’s a hole for you to nail in plastic covers, but it does not come with them. I think I also would’ve liked the metal piece that the door hit (in the middle) would’ve been magnetic or something to keep the doors firmly shut. Overall I am still really happy with this purchase and how it looks.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for board games!
reviews.reviewText: I am so incredibly happy with this purchase! The seller reached out to inform us what to expect with shipping, which was very appreciated. The shipping speed was decent, I ordered Dec. 24 and it arrived Dec 29/30. The two units shipped separately and arrived within a day of each other, which I appreciated because it was nice to have a break in between putting them together. It was quite easy to assemble, we had no issues with the hinges or doors like the other reviews suggested, a drill was much more efficient vs a screw driver. We had all the hardware needed. The pieces were packaged very well and did not get any damage during shipping.I love the soft close feature of the doors. I highly recommend this unit. Great storage space and very aesthetic.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 24, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for storage
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this to house my albums and record player. It’s perfect. The shelf on the inside is adjustable so the albums fit on the bottom with the top shelf available for other storage. Assembly was easy and directions were clear. Dimensions and materials true as advertised. Good piece of furniture at its price point.

reviews.reviewText: This product is very flimsy , it is not stable it moves from side to side and made of cheap materials. The seller is so unprofessional. I am missing 4 specialty screws, brackets are bent and there is a gap in front which should not be there . Seller is non cooperative. I requested a refund and I was told I would not get one without photos proving the issues. Then told I would be responsible for the shipping costs. This has been A horrible experience, I would not recommend purchasing from this seller.

reviews.reviewText: This is one of my new favorite pieces of furniture! Assembly was easy and it seems sturdy enough. I use mine for towel storage next to our bathroom. It was slightly bigger than expected, as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Instructions need words not just pictures
reviews.reviewText: While I do like this product, I’m quite disappointed in the instructions when putting this product together. As a novice in putting furniture together, I do Ile picture directions, but some parts needed some word directions. Thankfully my husband helped me and explained how to use some of the screws. You see, they weren’t just screws, but they required some knowledge in using them. Knowledge that was not in the directions. Please consider improving the instructions. That would help many of us.
